					<p class="style22">o&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;melted then cast into blocks</p>
					<p class="style22">o&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;sintered into blocks, sintered roadways</p>
					<p class="style22">o&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;fiberglass, fiber mats</p>
					<p class="style22">o&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cast glass, ceramics</p>
					<p class="style22">o&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;metals for conducting wire, machinery, structural 
