					<p class="style17">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Building material for habitats, garages, berms, 
					landing pads, roadways.</p>
					<p class="style17">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Protection from radiation and as a thermal 
					insulator.</p>
					<p class="style17">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Raw material for solar cell and solar 
					concentrators</p>
					<p class="style17">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;For extraction of trace elements, such as C and 
					N</p>
					
					<p class="style17">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Helium 3 for fusion power</p>
				<p class="style17">&nbsp;</p>
					<p class="style17">Resources: Solar Radiation<o:p></o:p></p>
					<p class="style17">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Solar energy from solar cells and solar 
					collectors</p>
					<p class="style17">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Temperature difference from shadow to sunlight 
