				Concept of Operations define a new system for that particular 
				phase of the process.&nbsp;&nbsp;Before a phase can be completed the 
				student team must also consider the &quot;Other SE Functions&quot; (6 through 11)<strong>;
				</strong>the consideration can be a brief one if the function 
				does not warrant a significant effort.&nbsp;&nbsp; Each function 
				is explained below.</p>
